    @Generated(value="com.guidewire.pl.metadata.codegen.Codegen",
           comments="CommonContactContact.eti;CommonContactContact.eix;CommonContactContact.etx")
public interface CommonContactContact
extends Bean
    CommonContactContact Allows code to operate on those common properties held by either ContactContact or ABContactContact. This is a shared delegate/interface that allows code-sharing in cases where code might be used by both ContactManager and another Guidewire application.
